7z6A3_SOErAA">Tu Vân Lâm xã Pháp Vân tự - 修雲林社法雲寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%A3i-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-6cYWLQesK-1k0z0R4lQAWw">Phạm Đãi Đán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Tu%C3%BD-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Phi-c%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-RLqWEtKjhq9ylzlly3Z4EA">Tuý Dương Phi cúc kỳ 2 - 醉楊妃菊其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-nguy%C3%AAn-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-6qvbBFPqKGw1jJEFfSUB_Q">Xuân nguyên hữu cảm kỳ 1 - 春元有感其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Y%E1%BA%BFt-m%C3%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-K%C3%ADnh-s%C6%A1n/poem-0AkzNfaKnmLDn7lY2rM5xQ">Yết mã Đại Kính sơn - 歇馬大徑山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-s3x28VNwVFO_JS6LZ5Jo0w">Trần Hiến Chương</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
